{
    "esm": "0.4.0",
    "metadata": {
        "name": "HoltslagBovilleLocalDiffusion",
        "description": "Local boundary-layer diffusion scheme of Holtslag & Boville (1993) — eddy diffusivity from local gradients of wind and virtual potential temperature, via a height-dependent mixing length and a Richardson-number stability function. Migrated from AtmosphericDynamics.jl@816cc391 src/holtslag_boville_1993.jl:184 (`HoltslagBovilleLocalDiffusion` @component).",
        "tags": [
            "atmospheric_dynamics",
            "holtslag-boville",
            "boundary-layer",
            "eddy-diffusivity",
            "local-diffusion"
        ],
        "created": "2026-05-17T00:00:00Z",
        "authors": [
            "AtmosphericDynamics.jl contributors",
            "EarthSciModels migration (esm-279z)"
        ],
        "references": [
            {
                "doi": "10.1175/1520-0442(1993)006<1825:LVNBLD>2.0.CO;2",
                "citation": "Holtslag, A. A. M., & Boville, B. A. (1993). Local Versus Nonlocal Boundary-Layer Diffusion in a Global Climate Model. Journal of Climate, 6(10), 1825-1842. Section 3 (Local diffusion scheme): Eq. 3.2 (eddy diffusivity), 3.3 (local shear), 3.4 (mixing length), 3.5 (gradient Richardson number), 3.6 (asymptotic length scale), 3.7 (unstable stability function); Eq. 2.11 (stable stability function)."
            }
        ]
    },
    "models": {
        "HoltslagBovilleLocalDiffusion": {
            "reference": {
                "notes": "source_ref: AtmosphericDynamics.jl@816cc391:src/holtslag_boville_1993.jl:184\n\nHoltslagBovilleLocalDiffusion is an MTK `@component` implementing the local boundary-layer diffusion scheme of Holtslag & Boville (1993), Journal of Climate 6, 1825-1842, Section 3. The six equations are the asymptotic length scale (Eq. 3.6), the harmonic mixing length (Eq. 3.4), the local shear magnitude (Eq. 3.3), the gradient Richardson number (Eq. 3.5), the stability function (Eq. 3.7 unstable / Eq. 2.11 stable), and the eddy diffusivity (Eq. 3.2). All six are algebraic diagnostics — there is no ODE integration.\n\nConstants: the upstream `@constants` g, κ, z_ref, λ_min, λ_range, S_min, and zero_Ri are serialized as parameter-type variables with fixed defaults — the .esm schema has no dedicated constant variable type, and physical constants are carried as parameters. This mirrors the GeneralCirculation and ScaleHeight migrations from the same upstream package.\n\nVariable names: the upstream Unicode identifiers are kept verbatim (θᵥ, ∂θᵥ_∂z, ∂u_∂z, ∂v_∂z, λc, λ_min, λ_range, κ) — mtk2esm serializes MTK symbols as-is and Unicode variable names are used throughout the committed .esm corpus.\n\nStability function: Fc is a two-branch `ifelse` on the sign of Ri. The unstable branch (Ri < 0) is Eq. 3.7, Fc = (1 - 18 Ri)^(1/2); since Ri < 0 there, 1 - 18 Ri > 1 and the square root is always real. The stable branch (Ri >= 0) is Eq. 2.11, Fc = 1/(1 + 10 Ri(1 + 8 Ri)); the denominator 1 + 10 Ri + 80 Ri^2 has no real roots, so it never vanishes. The branch boundary Ri = 0 evaluates the stable branch to exactly Fc = 1, matching the unstable-branch limit, so Fc is continuous.\n\nRegularization and finiteness: the shear S carries an additive floor S_min = 1e-6 1/s (upstream 'Minimum shear for regularization'), so Ri = (g/θᵥ)(∂θᵥ/∂z)/S^2 and Kc stay finite even at zero wind shear. The mixing length lc = 1/(1/(κ z) + 1/λc) tends to 0 (not 0/0) as z -> 0. There is no singular test point for this component, so every inline test asserts at its nominal parameter values.\n\nTolerance rationale (rel=1e-6, abs=1e-9): an algebraic diagnostic system with no ODE integration. rel=1e-6 covers float64 round-off in the closed-form exp / sqrt / divide chain; abs=1e-9 covers the intended exact zero (Ri = 0 in the neutral_richardson test, where ∂θᵥ/∂z = 0 makes the numerator identically zero)."
            },
            "tolerance": {
                "rel": 1e-06,
                "abs": 1e-09
            },
            "variables": {
                "g": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m/s^2",
                    "default": 9.81,
                    "description": "Gravitational acceleration"
                },
                "κ": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 0.4,
                    "description": "von Karman constant (dimensionless)"
                },
                "z_ref": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 1000.0,
                    "description": "Reference height for λc calculation (Eq. 3.6)"
                },
                "λ_min": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 30.0,
                    "description": "Free atmosphere asymptotic length scale (Eq. 3.6)"
                },
                "λ_range": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 270.0,
                    "description": "Range of asymptotic length scale (Eq. 3.6)"
                },
                "S_min": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 1e-06,
                    "description": "Minimum shear for regularization"
                },
                "zero_Ri": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Zero Richardson number for comparison"
                },
                "z": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 100.0,
                    "description": "Height above surface"
                },
                "θᵥ": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K",
                    "default": 300.0,
                    "description": "Virtual potential temperature"
                },
                "∂θᵥ_∂z": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K/m",
                    "default": 0.003,
                    "description": "Vertical gradient of virtual potential temperature"
                },
                "∂u_∂z": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 0.01,
                    "description": "Vertical gradient of zonal wind"
                },
                "∂v_∂z": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Vertical gradient of meridional wind"
                },
                "λc": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "m",
                    "description": "Asymptotic length scale (Eq. 3.6)"
                },
                "lc": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "m",
                    "description": "Mixing length scale (Eq. 3.4)"
                },
                "S": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "description": "Local wind shear magnitude (Eq. 3.3)"
                },
                "Ri": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Gradient Richardson number (Eq. 3.5) (dimensionless)"
                },
                "Fc": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Stability function (Eq. 3.7/2.11) (dimensionless)"
                },
                "Kc": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "m^2/s",
                    "description": "Eddy diffusivity (Eq. 3.2)"
                }
            },
            "equations": [
                {
                    "lhs": "λc",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "+",
                        "args": [
                            "λ_min",
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    "λ_range",
                                    {
                                        "op": "exp",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "-",
                                                "args": [
                                                    1,
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "/",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            "z",
                                                            "z_ref"
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "lc",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            1,
                            {
                                "op": "+",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "/",
                                        "args": [
                                            1,
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": [
                                                    "κ",
                                                    "z"
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "op": "/",
                                        "args": [
                                            1,
                                            "λc"
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "S",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "+",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "sqrt",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "+",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "^",
                                                "args": [
                                                    "∂u_∂z",
                                                    2
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "op": "^",
                                                "args": [
                                                    "∂v_∂z",
                                                    2
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            "S_min"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "Ri",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "/",
                                        "args": [
                                            "g",
                                            "θᵥ"
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "∂θᵥ_∂z"
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "op": "^",
                                "args": [
                                    "S",
                                    2
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "Fc",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "ifelse",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "<",
                                "args": [
                                    "Ri",
                                    "zero_Ri"
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "op": "sqrt",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "-",
                                        "args": [
                                            1,
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": [
                                                    18,
                                                    "Ri"
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "op": "/",
                                "args": [
                                    1,
                                    {
                                        "op": "+",
                                        "args": [
                                            1,
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": [
                                                    10,
                                                    "Ri",
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "+",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            1,
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "*",
                                                                "args": [
                                                                    8,
                                                                    "Ri"
                                                                ]
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
